  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to determine the influence of the periodontal diseases in patients
      giving pre-term birth in the maternity hospital of Nantes. A French population is observed.
      The clinical, bacteriological and microbiological aspects will confirmed a comparative study
      which aim is dental prevention in the beginning of the pregnancy to avoid premature delivery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
